
                       M U N I N  -  M Y S Q L
                      =========================


Munin plugin for showing graphs of MySQL resource usage.


INSTALLATION
------------

 1) Install dependencies
 
     - munin-node
     - Perl modules: DBI, DBD::mysql, and Cache::Cache
 
 2) Edit Makefile
 
 3) Edit mysql_.conf
 
 4) Run `make install'


